snippet.title: L'Oreal Infallible Amber Rush
snippet.description:
L’Oréal 24HR Infallible Eye Shadow in Amber Rush Makeup Tutorial

Here’s another makeup tutorial that is great to wear to Homecoming.  Try this look out!  I hope you all enjoy this tutorial and have fun watching it :) All the products and brushes used are listed below!  Be sure to subscribe to my channel makeupbytavao, and also make sure to check out my IG, Twitter, Facebook, and beauty blog.



Check out my Basics Tutorials here:

UPDATED Eyebrow Tutorial
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oN6Txmy6l7g&list=PLTkgSesRq0oc1OGpCD8LBcUlX_IPQRK5Z

UPDATED Foundation Tutorial
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9lQdAExaiI&index=5&list=PLTkgSesRq0oc1OGpCD8LBcUlX_IPQRK5Z

Highlight using Concealer
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aLYVMdbefpg&list=PLTkgSesRq0oc1OGpCD8LBcUlX_IPQRK5Z&index=6

Contouring the Face with Powder
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P0gtJtTp-ik&index=7&list=PLTkgSesRq0oc1OGpCD8LBcUlX_IPQRK5Z

Contouring with Cream
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9nrpBgkIds4&list=PLTkgSesRq0oc1OGpCD8LBcUlX_IPQRK5Z


Make sure to check out:
Artist Couture by Angel Moreno Diamond Glow Powders
http://www.artistcouture.com/collections/diamond-glow-powder



PRODUCTS USED:

Eyes -
LORAC Behind the Scenes Eye Primer http://www.loraccosmetics.com/make-up_behind-the-scenes.html
MAC Soft Brown http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/154/363/Products/Eyes/Shadow/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl
MAC Swiss Chocolate http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/154/363/Products/Eyes/Shadow/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl
LORAC Front of the Line PRO Liquid Eyeliner Black http://www.ulta.com/ulta/browse/productDetail.jsp?productId=xlsImpprod1400042#
Burberry Beauty ‘Effortless Mascara’ Volumising Enhancer No. 01 Midnight Black http://shop.nordstrom.com/s/burberry-beauty-effortless-mascara-volumising-enhancer/3118746?origin=category-personalizedsort&contextualcategoryid=0&fashionColor=&resultback=534&cm_sp=personalizedsort-_-browseresults-_-1_1_B


Face -
Artist Couture Diamond Glow Powder Mermaid Fantasy
http://www.artistcouture.com/collections/diamond-glow-powder/products/mermaid-fantasy


Lips -
MAC Pro Longwear Lip Pencil Etcetera http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/167/17337/Products/Lips/Lip-Pencil/Pro-Longwear-Lip-Pencil/index.tmpl
Yves Saint Laurent Rouge Volupte 04 Sweet Honey
Estée Lauder Pure Color High Gloss 01 Crystal Clear


Brushes/Tools -
Sigma E40 Copper http://www.sigmabeauty.com/E40_Tapered_Blending_Copper_p/e40c.htm
Tom Ford #11 Eyeshadow Brush http://shop.nordstrom.com/s/tom-ford-eyeshadow-brush/3622598?origin=keywordsearch-personalizedsort&contextualcategoryid=2375500&fashionColor=&resultback=1320&cm_sp=personalizedsort-_-searchresults-_-1_4_D
